WEBVTT

00:00:00.535 --> 00:00:02.621
nayn hundert nayntsik zibn

00:00:03.268 --> 00:00:07.143
der ibergelebter di katastrofye iz Khaim ZILVANSKI

00:00:07.842 --> 00:00:11.042
un der TAPE iz numer fir.

00:00:13.258 --> 00:00:16.492
shtelt undz for ver zitst lebn aykh.

00:00:17.258 --> 00:00:19.446
lebn mir zitst mayn froy

00:00:19.452 --> 00:00:21.572
ROSA ZELWIANSKI.

00:00:21.713 --> 00:00:24.761
ir meydlsher nomen iz Poyker.

00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:26.654
mir hobn

00:00:26.654 --> 00:00:27.933
mit ir

00:00:28.362 --> 00:00:29.790
tsvey kinder

00:00:29.593 --> 00:00:30.785
ven ⟨hot ir⟩ khasene gehat?

00:00:30.555 --> 00:00:35.240
a zun mit a tokhter. khasene gehat hobn mir in akht un fertsiktn yor

00:00:35.314 --> 00:00:37.130
in der shtot Babroysk.

00:00:41.575 --> 00:00:43.394
vos

00:00:43.394 --> 00:00:44.758
vilt ir tsum

00:00:45.135 --> 00:00:49.469
ende tsu vos, dem intervyu, ⟨vos volt ir⟩ nokh veln

00:00:49.469 --> 00:00:50.647
epes zogn

00:00:51.143 --> 00:00:52.791
far di mentshheyt?

00:00:52.594 --> 00:00:55.996
ikh vil zogn far dem gantser mentshheyt

00:00:56.070 --> 00:01:01.599
az keyn mol zol keyner nisht visn fun a shreklekher mageyfe

00:01:01.656 --> 00:01:03.669
nor ikh vil zogn eyn zakh

00:01:03.669 --> 00:01:05.564
az tsu vintsik

00:01:05.605 --> 00:01:08.820
dertseylt men far undzere kinder mit di eyniklekh

00:01:08.820 --> 00:01:10.980
fun der shreklekher katastrofye.

00:01:11.072 --> 00:01:12.107
me darf g-

00:01:12.107 --> 00:01:15.769
vos mer filmen, vos mer dertseyln zey

00:01:15.769 --> 00:01:19.633
vayle der shraybn vos me shraybt, yidishe shrayber shraybn

00:01:19.633 --> 00:01:21.185
dos gleybt men nisht.

00:01:21.185 --> 00:01:24.156
dos meynt men az a shrayber shraybt nor far gelt

00:01:24.156 --> 00:01:25.798
ober ven es kumt der

00:01:25.888 --> 00:01:28.450
eydes, der lebediker eydes

00:01:28.450 --> 00:01:31.597
un dertseylt zey az er hot es aleyn durkhgelebt

00:01:31.597 --> 00:01:35.765
er hot dos aleyn durkhgemakht ot o di shvere, shreklekhe mageyfe

00:01:35.765 --> 00:01:37.234
demolt gleybt men.

00:01:37.234 --> 00:01:38.842
un ir darft

00:01:38.865 --> 00:01:41.022
⟨ir d-⟩ bney rakhmonim

00:01:41.022 --> 00:01:42.667
ir darft zen

00:01:42.667 --> 00:01:44.591
az s- ot o dos alts

00:01:44.591 --> 00:01:47.057
zol dergeyn tsu undzere kinder

00:01:47.057 --> 00:01:48.867
un tsu undzere eyniklekh

00:01:48.867 --> 00:01:51.947
un tsu undzere kind's kind's kinder.

00:01:51.947 --> 00:01:54.514
ir darft oysnitsn ot o di

00:01:54.514 --> 00:01:55.965
eyntslne

00:01:55.965 --> 00:01:57.264
mentshn

00:01:57.264 --> 00:02:01.036
velkhe zaynen geblibn lebn nokh fun dem shreklekhn khurbn

00:02:01.036 --> 00:02:02.392
az zey zaynen

00:02:02.392 --> 00:02:04.732
di emese lebedike eydes

00:02:04.732 --> 00:02:06.802
velkhe kenen dos aleyn dervayzn.

00:02:06.844 --> 00:02:09.982
demolt geyt es tsu nenter tsum hartsn

00:02:09.982 --> 00:02:11.722
far undzere kinder

00:02:11.722 --> 00:02:13.220
far undzere eyniklekh

00:02:13.220 --> 00:02:16.340
vayle dos darfn visn nisht nor undzere kinder.

00:02:16.340 --> 00:02:19.420
dos darfn visn di eyniklekh un ureyniklekh

00:02:19.420 --> 00:02:21.500
un ur ureyniklekh

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:23.140
az aza mageyfe

00:02:23.140 --> 00:02:26.060
zol shoyn keyn mol nisht forkumen

00:02:26.060 --> 00:02:29.824
un demolt vet got rakhmones hobn oyf dem yidishn folk

00:02:29.824 --> 00:02:32.136
KERAKHEM OV AL BONIM

00:02:32.136 --> 00:02:35.272
KEN TIRAKHEM ADOYNOY OLEYNU.

00:02:36.595 --> 00:02:37.821
a dank aykh.

00:02:40.037 --> 00:02:41.853
onrufn UNK dertseyln.

00:02:45.133 --> 00:02:47.152
dos iz mayn foter.

00:02:47.682 --> 00:02:50.173
er ruft zikh Zorekh ZELWIANSKI.

00:02:52.930 --> 00:02:54.966
der foter

00:02:55.647 --> 00:02:59.455
iz umgekumen in tsayt fun der shreklekher mageyfe.

00:03:00.608 --> 00:03:02.576
ven iz di foto genumen gevorn?

00:03:02.363 --> 00:03:07.807
di foto iz genumen gevorn shoyn nokh der milkhome fun mayn shvester velkhe lebt in Argentine.

00:03:07.932 --> 00:03:09.951
dos hot ir genumen di foto.

00:03:09.957 --> 00:03:12.094
un ven hot men im gemakht di foto?

00:03:11.948 --> 00:03:13.916
ven? far der milkhome.

00:03:17.770 --> 00:03:19.226
dos bin ikh

00:03:19.226 --> 00:03:20.936
Khaim ZELWIANSKI.

00:03:21.955 --> 00:03:22.961
dos iz

00:03:22.967 --> 00:03:23.714
gesh-

00:03:23.714 --> 00:03:25.559
foto gemakht gevorn

00:03:25.802 --> 00:03:30.706
ven ikh bin arayngetrotn in dem yidishn teater fun Ester Rokhl Kaminski

00:03:30.882 --> 00:03:33.913
ven ikh hob nokh gelebt far der milkhome in Poyln.

00:03:35.488 --> 00:03:37.540
vi iz tsu aykh gekumen di foto?

00:03:37.497 --> 00:03:39.566
di foto iz geblibn

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:41.523
in Argentine

00:03:42.053 --> 00:03:43.433
bay der shvester

00:03:43.433 --> 00:03:45.084
velkhe ikh hob es tsugenumen.

00:03:50.423 --> 00:03:53.668
fun links oyf rekhts, dos iz mayn froy

00:03:53.668 --> 00:03:55.496
ROSA ZELWIANSKI.

00:03:55.873 --> 00:03:57.875
lebn ir shteyt mayn zun

00:03:57.882 --> 00:04:00.120
Zorekh ZELWIANSKI

00:04:00.379 --> 00:04:02.257
dernokh mayn tokhter

00:04:02.257 --> 00:04:04.136
ANNA ZELWIANSKI.

00:04:04.260 --> 00:04:06.585
un dos bin ikh aleyn.

00:04:06.585 --> 00:04:08.422
Khaim ZELWIANSKI.

00:04:08.901 --> 00:04:11.426
di foto iz gemakht gevorn

00:04:11.955 --> 00:04:13.957
in di zekhtsikter yorn

00:04:15.364 --> 00:04:19.863
un hot zikh gefunen bay mayn shvester in Argentine fun velkher ikh hob tsugenumen.

00:04:25.371 --> 00:04:28.638
dos iz mayn froy ROSA ZELWIANSKI.

00:04:29.100 --> 00:04:32.604
lebn ir shteyt mayn tokhter ANNA ZELWIANSKI.

00:04:33.100 --> 00:04:36.801
dos bild iz gemakht gevorn in di zekhtsikter yorn

00:04:36.801 --> 00:04:38.494
in dem shtot Babroysk.

00:04:43.815 --> 00:04:45.007
dos iz

00:04:45.216 --> 00:04:46.461
der ort

00:04:46.461 --> 00:04:48.517
vu es zaynen umgekumen

00:04:48.760 --> 00:04:52.922
mayne eltern un di gantse mishpokhe mayne

00:04:53.485 --> 00:04:55.521
un nokh hunderter

00:04:55.527 --> 00:04:57.343
toyznter yidn

00:04:57.450 --> 00:04:59.756
do shteyt der ondenkung

00:04:59.796 --> 00:05:01.337
az mentshn

00:05:01.337 --> 00:05:03.109
zoln gedenken

00:05:03.109 --> 00:05:05.950
az s'iz geshen ot o di shreklekhe mageyfe.

00:05:06.175 --> 00:05:09.139
vu iz dos, der ondenk, di, di matseyve?

00:05:08.267 --> 00:05:09.982
in shtetele Mir

00:05:10.815 --> 00:05:11.872
Mir

00:05:12.013 --> 00:05:14.153
vos gefint zikh lebn Baranovitsh.

00:05:18.578 --> 00:05:19.334
THAT'S IT.
